\begin{figure}[t]
\centering
\includegraphics[width=\textwidth]{figures/phase1_isolate.pdf}
\caption{Null Model~A knob isolation. Each panel shows the MC null distribution (blue) against the observed value (red dashed). Adding running shifts the observed result from the tail toward the centre of the null distribution.}
